{"tid":944642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶)呢張相我睇到喊。。。。","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T10:41:50.000Z","uid":201143,"like":22,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07e5777ab9bd69849d3d4192badfd90dc2c40495","tid":944642,"uid":201143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"睇完台慶好心噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我始終都覺得洪永城同黃翠如最襯...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20151024/s00009/1445698806000SF_E0ABDA41CDC539E626FDFDDE2CA2EBEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20151024%2Fs00009%2F1445698806000SF_E0ABDA41CDC539E626FDFDDE2CA2EBEF.jpg&h=e1bc0137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗每個男人心裡面都有一個黃翠如 <br />\n<br />\n有D男人頭，有D亂黎，你同佢好Friend <br />\n會一齊食飯 一齊宵夜 一齊去旅行 <br />\n但係永遠唔會撻著 <br />\n<br />\n你同佢好似總係有D莫名嘅共鳴 <br />\n人地永遠會以為你地係一對 <br />\n但你心裡面知道根本無可能 <br />\n當朋友問到 <br />\n你通常都答 「Hi 係有D好感 但係當佢係friend黎嫁咋」 <br />\n<br />\n但係問心 <br />\n你係有小小鍾意佢 <br />\n但你亦知道 <br />\n佢係完全唔鍾意你 <br />\n<br />\n你地都好享受呢種感覺 <br />\n一種好似男女朋友咁親密 但係完全無男女朋友責任嘅感覺 <br />\n<br />\n直到一日黃翠如同蕭正楠係埋一齊 <br />\n你會發覺 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「Hi原來我好鍾意黃翠如呢條八婆」 <br />\n<br />\n但係好可惜你已經失去左一百次同黃翠如一齊嘅機會 <br />\n你只好係成班friend面前繼續同黃翠如扮好朋友 <br />\n得閒串下佢 佢得閒 佢得閒又會串番下你 <br />\n但係你兩個都知 其實有d野係唔同左 <br />\n<br />\n難得有一次工作上嘅機會 <br />\n你可以再同黃翠如手拖手。。。 <br />\n<br />\n隔左一兩日 <br />\n你睇番報紙 <br />\n見到張相 <br />\n你微笑 <br />\n<br />\n你流淚 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd862fa9740277857b6941e84f9b80aa48b1de1","tid":944642,"uid":201143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"好驚會變做洪永城<br />\n睇住自己鍾意嘅人喺婚禮度<br />\n但主角唔係自己<br />\n淨係可以喺隔離拍手...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d79a6f594f0805be0bdf4bf2bf31e7c3798eb9","tid":944642,"uid":214458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"一頭蠻牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331aa6c9911c447d6707384fc00a02ed6c624a59","tid":944642,"uid":30006,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔好痴線啦<br />\n<br />\n係你地d人一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊要好多野，唔係你外人覺得個樣夾就要一齊<br />\n<br />\n你睇完電視拍拍屎忽行左去，人地要對一世<br />\n<br />\n雖然我認同佢兩個襯d，不過唔會反應大成咁"},{"pid":"cbb7b011c0f4bac0250c7eeada62a781c6a4c7e7","tid":944642,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"唔好癲啦<br />\n我鍾意陳法拉<br />\n法拉BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e625a03a86c9d58fd88501d9cb5344d79e914a","tid":944642,"uid":201143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331aa6c9911c447d6707384fc00a02ed6c624a59","tid":944642,"uid":30006,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔好痴線啦<br />\n<br />\n係你地d人一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n兩個人一齊要好多野，唔係你外人覺得個樣夾就要一齊<br />\n<br />\n你睇完電視拍拍屎忽行左去，人地要對一世<br />\n<br />\n雖然我認同佢兩個襯d，不過唔會反應大成咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"覺得有啲可惜啫...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6984113f9047177ec289127020876f2bb12d30","tid":944642,"uid":201143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb7b011c0f4bac0250c7eeada62a781c6a4c7e7","tid":944642,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"唔好癲啦<br />\n我鍾意陳法拉<br />\n法拉BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"Wrong channel"},{"pid":"0dcf0186c0befa139d24779f1da432f96375d01d","ti